PrecisRe-appointment of GORDON HANDCOCK, of Mount Pearl, Newfoundland, as a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of Newfoundland to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective May 2, 1998.
